FuncDef: The undo acl ipv6 name command deletes a created ACL6. The undo acl ipv6 name command deletes a created ACL6. By default, no ACL6 is created.

ParaDef.Info:
Creates an ACL6 with a name.
The value is a string of 1 to 32 case-sensitive characters, spaces not supported.

ExtraInfo: To create an ACL6, run the acl ipv6 command.
